                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#3r">f. 3r</locus>
                           <desc type="DonationNote">Donation note.</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">
                              ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘወሀባ፡ ደጀዝማች፡ ኀጎስ፡ ዳግማዊ፡ ዘመንፈስ፡
                              ቅዱስ፡ ለታቦተ፡ ማርያም፡ ዘፈቃዳ።<foreign xml:lang="en">This (is) the book which daǧǧāzmāč
                              Ḫagos (of ) Za-Manfas Qǝddus the Second donated to the church of Mary
                              of Faqādā.</foreign></q><note>  <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4996hagosSa">Ḫagos</persName> (d. 1831), baptismal name Dāgǝmāwi Za-Manfas
                                 Qǝddus, is probably the second son of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8265Sabagadi">daǧǧāzmāč Sabāgādis</persName> whose
                              baptismal name is Za-Manfas Qǝddus (b. 1780/85, d. 1831, s. EAE IV,
                              431). The note is written in the same hand as Additio 2. </note>
                          
                              
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
